{
  "stem": "17845.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 18.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "She said, look, they were talking about they're going to bombard Bilgoraj.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I mean, as soon as she pronounced that word, a bomb fall into our kitchen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "That was the first bomb which really fall into our city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And it was just, I think, a miracle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Because 3 o'clock, we would have sit, five of us at the dinner table, having lunch.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It made a big hole in our kitchen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And the whole city came running afterwards looking what happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And the burgermeister came, and everybody they could not believe it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "That a family of five, 3 o'clock in the afternoon survived something like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And, of course, we didn't have anymore where to sleep.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "So we went to stay with my grandfather for a few days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He-- to stay at his house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, not far.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whole of Bilgoraj wasn't a big, big place, so not far.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we stayed with him for a few days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then in our city, actually out of the city was living a Mr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Miller.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was of German origin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they would start talking that he is a German spy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And somehow managed to-- they managed to put arson around all Bilgoraj.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, Bilgoraj started burning, after-- 10 days after the war started.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we all started running to the river.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because that's only way that we thought we might survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when we arrived there, my father remembered that the Sefer Torah was hidden in our place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he wrapped a blanket, and my mother was begging him, please don't go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because Bilgoraj was burning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You couldn't-- but he wouldn't listen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He says, I'm not going to let the Sefer Torah burning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I'm just not going to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "If I can save it, I will.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
